# Join Dots Game - Implementation Plan

A visually stunning Connect Four game with AI integration powered by window.ai.complete, featuring smooth animations, glassmorphism design, and three difficulty levels.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This implementation uses **window.ai.complete** for AI opponent logic. This API requires Chrome with built-in AI capabilities or a compatible browser extension. The game will gracefully handle cases where the API is unavailable.

> [!NOTE]
> The game will be built as a single-page React application using Vite for fast development and Tailwind CSS for styling. All game logic runs client-side with no backend required.

